-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;=
">dynamic=C2=A0hedging of inverse exchange-traded notes on volatility index=
es</a>, but that=E2=80=99s not how finance works anymore. =E2=80=9CDon't fo=
rget to pencil in the SNL opening as a key market event risk for next week,=
=E2=80=9D <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/23761771=
