tyle: solid; background-color: #ccc;">tweeted Bloomberg=E2=80=99s Tracy All=
oway</a>.</p><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">In the last=C2=A0dumb, dumb year =
I have proposed two very dumb theories of financial markets, both of which =
seem relevant to Dogecoin:</p><ol style=3D"list-style-type: decimal; paddin=
g-left: 40px; margin: 16px 0;">=09<li style=3D"margin-bottom: 5px;">The <a =
href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/23761771.258996/aHR0c=
