 style=3D"color: #000000; text-decoration: none !important; border-bottom-w=
idth: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; backgr=
ound-color: #ccc;"> what I focused on</a>: As a story of startup hype and o=
verpromising to investors, the Theranos Inc. story didn=E2=80=99t seem all =
